name: XCPCARD, june 24th 2015 , Spell Of Genesis EPIC card, Counterparty XCP NFT Asset
description:
XCPCARD was issued on the blockchain (june 24th 2015) by the first blockchain NFT collectibles : the game called Spell of Genesis. 
This legendary collection of NFTs was minted on Counterparty (XCP), long before the barrage of normie NFTs we see today. Many Counterparty wallets have been lost over the years, thus circulation is far lower than the issuance. Inspect the goods:

https://xchain.io/asset/XCPCARD

Counterparty assets live in the OP_RETURN section of the Bitcoin blockchain. 
CYBERPUNK88 does the hard part for you, acquiring the assets and wrapping them in emblem.finance vaults. Verify the asset is in this vault by clicking the BTC address link in the description.

MORE SpellsOfGenesis cards : https://opensea.io/CYBERPUNK88
